kers since the 16th century and has been particularly favoured since the 1980s."],"variants":[{"name":"Danyal","meanings":["Fanciful respelling of   Daniel ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Daniel Fisc I was born in 1170, in Laxfield, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom, his father, Henry Fisc, was 16 and his mother, Mrs Henry Fisc, was 19. He had at least 1 son with Mrs Daniel Fisc. He died in 1208, in his hometown, at the age of 38, and was buried in Laxfield, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1170–1208":"1170–1208","1181–Female":"1181–Surnud","1208–1258":"1208–1258","1154–1189":"1154–1189","1152–Female":"1152–Surnud","1258":"1258","1189":"1189","1154":"1154","1152":"1152","1170":"1170","1208":"1208","1181":"1181","All Saints Churchyard, Laxfield, Mid Suffolk District, Suffolk, England":"Laxfield, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Laxfield, Suffolk, England":"Laxfield, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1170–1208":"1170–1208","1181–Female":"1181–Kuollut","1208–1258":"1208–1258","1154–1189":"1154–1189","1152–Female":"1152–Kuollut","1258":"1258","1189":"1189","1154":"1154","1152":"1152","1170":"1170","1208":"1208","1181":"1181","All Saints Churchyard, Laxfield, Mid Suffolk District, Suffolk, England":"Laxfield, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Laxfield, Suffolk, England":"Laxfield, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1170–1208":"1170–1208","1181–Female":"1181–Décédée","1208–1258":"1208–1258","1154–1189":"1154–1189","1152–Female":"1152–Décédée","1258":"1258","1189":"1189","1154":"1154","1152":"1152","1170":"1170","1208":"1208","1181":"1181","All Saints Churchyard, Laxfield, Mid Suffolk District, Suffolk, England":"Laxfield, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Laxfield, Suffolk, England":"Laxfield, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Daniel Fisc I est né en 1170, à Laxfield, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, Henry Fisc, avait 16 ans et sa mère, Mrs Henry Fisc, avait 19 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils